     1ŌåÆ# Contributing
     3ŌåÆ1. [Fork it](https://help.github.com/articles/fork-a-repo/)
     4ŌåÆ2. Install dependencies (`npm install`)
     5ŌåÆ3. Create your feature branch (`git checkout -b my-new-feature`)
     6ŌåÆ4. Commit your changes (`git commit -am 'Added some feature'`)
     7ŌåÆ5. Test your changes (`npm test`)
     8ŌåÆ6. Push to the branch (`git push origin my-new-feature`)
     9ŌåÆ7. [Create new Pull Request](https://help.github.com/articles/creating-a-pull-request/)
    10ŌåÆ
    11ŌåÆ## Testing
    13ŌåÆWe use [TAP](https://github.com/tapjs/node-tap) to write tests. Run our test suite with this command:
    14ŌåÆ
    15ŌåÆ```
    16ŌåÆnpm test
    17ŌåÆ```
    18ŌåÆ
    19ŌåÆ## Code Style
    21ŌåÆWe use [standard](https://www.npmjs.com/package/standard) and [editorconfig](http://editorconfig.org) to maintain code style and best practices. Please make sure your PR adheres to the guides by running:
    22ŌåÆ
    23ŌåÆ```
    24ŌåÆnpm run lint
    25ŌåÆ```
